1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:08,790 --> 00:00:09,870
My name is

3
00:00:12,030 --> 00:00:12,990
Bai Li.

4
00:00:13,990 --> 00:00:16,870
Can I call you whenever I need you?

5
00:00:17,230 --> 00:00:19,520
You can contact me anytime if you need anything.

6
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:22,750
Who is the person that woke up in Bai Li's body?

7
00:00:23,350 --> 00:00:27,190
Ning Mochen.

8
00:00:27,420 --> 00:00:28,830
Tell me who you are.

9
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:31,040
I told you not to provoke her.

10
00:00:36,390 --> 00:00:38,150
Hurry up and look at the comments.

11
00:00:38,150 --> 00:00:39,880
Our comment section has been destroyed.

12
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:41,820
It's full of comments calling them bitches.

13
00:00:41,820 --> 00:00:43,330
What are you going to do?

14
00:00:43,510 --> 00:00:45,350
Boss, this is a comic.

15
00:00:45,350 --> 00:00:46,110
It won't do.

16
00:00:47,150 --> 00:00:48,150
If you talk like this,

17
00:00:48,150 --> 00:00:49,190
then I'll have to explain it to you.

18
00:00:49,190 --> 00:00:50,190
Are you dissing me again?

19
00:00:50,190 --> 00:00:51,790
-Are you dissing me again?
-No.

20
00:00:51,790 --> 00:00:52,870
-You are.
-I didn’t mean it that way.

21
00:00:52,870 --> 00:00:55,400
You don't want the rest of the payment, do you?

22
00:02:24,820 --> 00:02:28,860
[Perfect Her]

23
00:02:29,850 --> 00:02:32,120
[Episode 13]

24
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:37,430
Bai Li, look.

25
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:39,090
These are the design drafts

26
00:02:39,090 --> 00:02:41,420
you and Su Yu made together in university.

27
00:02:41,490 --> 00:02:42,210
Senior,

28
00:02:42,850 --> 00:02:45,310
we just want you to know about your past self.

29
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:47,150
We're not forcing you to remember anything.

30
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:47,790
Relax.

31
00:02:49,270 --> 00:02:50,510
Su Yu was

32
00:02:50,510 --> 00:02:51,910
one year below you in university,

33
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:54,150
but you two were the best partners.

34
00:02:54,390 --> 00:02:54,950
Yes.

35
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:55,990
Even now,

36
00:02:56,070 --> 00:02:58,710
I still remember the time when I drew

37
00:02:58,829 --> 00:03:00,790
and designed with you in university.

38
00:03:00,790 --> 00:03:01,550
At that time,

39
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,870
all we had to do was create imaginatively.

40
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:06,870
We weren't restricted by the client's requirements.

41
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:11,480
You are all here.

42
00:03:11,930 --> 00:03:13,350
Ning Mochen, why are you here?

43
00:03:13,350 --> 00:03:14,420
Su Yu called me.

44
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:17,240
I also want to help you regain your memory.

45
00:03:21,990 --> 00:03:22,630
Cha,

46
00:03:22,970 --> 00:03:24,120
I need to talk to you.

47
00:03:24,250 --> 00:03:25,850
Can you come out for a second?

48
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,520
Bai Li, wait for me.

49
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:29,930
I'll be right back.

50
00:03:37,890 --> 00:03:39,200
Was everything normal

51
00:03:39,390 --> 00:03:41,150
when you accompanied her yesterday?

52
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:42,480
What do you want to know?

53
00:03:43,650 --> 00:03:46,170
Cha, we've been through so much together.

54
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:47,470
Do you still think

55
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,950
we are not on the same side?

56
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:53,600
To be honest,

57
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:56,590
Bai Li's condition isn't optimistic.

58
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:58,360
What do you mean?

59
00:03:58,750 --> 00:04:01,070
Do you think someone's personality will change

60
00:04:01,070 --> 00:04:02,830
after losing their memory?

61
00:04:04,990 --> 00:04:05,880
I don't know,

62
00:04:06,420 --> 00:04:07,700
but I asked the doctor.

63
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:09,490
Even if one gets amnesia,

64
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:11,880
it's hard to change one's way of thinking

65
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,340
and subconscious habits.

66
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,030
Hello.

67
00:04:15,270 --> 00:04:17,070
Sorry to bother you, Dr. Peng.

68
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:19,970
I have a question.

69
00:04:20,790 --> 00:04:22,340
No problem. Go ahead.

70
00:04:22,990 --> 00:04:26,470
If a person loses their memory in an accident,

71
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:30,230
is there a possibility of them turning into someone else?

72
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:33,350
Technically, it's not likely,

73
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:36,920
but I've had some cases abroad

74
00:04:37,710 --> 00:04:41,630
where a person experiences something major.

75
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:44,720
Afterward, they can suddenly speak a language they didn't know

76
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:48,050
and do something they couldn't do before.

77
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:51,050
How can I stop them from becoming another person?

78
00:04:51,050 --> 00:04:52,490
Logically speaking,

79
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:55,150
you should have them remember who they are

80
00:04:55,409 --> 00:04:57,530
before they believe they're the other person,

81
00:04:57,530 --> 00:05:00,400
but it's hard to become another person,

82
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:04,580
because people's subconscious and habits are hard to change.

83
00:05:06,350 --> 00:05:07,620
You mean...

84
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:10,840
Did you think some details from her actions yesterday

85
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:12,330
weren't like Bai Li's?

86
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:15,630
Actually, I didn't sleep at her place last night.

87
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,930
She said she didn't want company.

88
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:20,890
She insisted that I leave.

89
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,810
She was very cold to me.

90
00:05:23,290 --> 00:05:26,220
To be honest, I've never seen Bai Li like this before.

91
00:05:27,350 --> 00:05:28,950
The Bai Li that Cha described

92
00:05:29,340 --> 00:05:32,000
is totally different from her pitiful look now.

93
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:34,680
Did she really lose her memory?

94
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,990
Do you remember these?

95
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:44,590
I heard people who lose their memories in an accident

96
00:05:44,590 --> 00:05:46,990
still won't forget their original skills.

97
00:05:47,530 --> 00:05:48,990
If you're given some time,

98
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:51,000
you should remember it slowly.

99
00:05:52,090 --> 00:05:54,980
I seem to remember something.

100
00:05:56,550 --> 00:05:57,159
Really?

101
00:05:58,550 --> 00:05:59,710
That's great.

102
00:06:02,490 --> 00:06:03,560
I need to take this.

103
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:10,480
The coffee here is good.

104
00:06:11,090 --> 00:06:12,620
Why aren't you drinking it?

105
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:21,460
Didn’t Su Yu say you’re left-handed?

106
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:24,630
Why are you using your right hand now?

107
00:06:29,670 --> 00:06:30,990
I don't think

108
00:06:30,990 --> 00:06:33,520
amnesia changes one's subconscious habits.

109
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:36,380
I guess.

110
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:46,040
What are you two talking about?

111
00:06:46,130 --> 00:06:46,960
Nothing.

112
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,140
Isn't she left-handed?

113
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:51,659
I found it strange that she used her right hand,

114
00:06:51,659 --> 00:06:52,580
so I asked.

115
00:06:52,870 --> 00:06:53,750
Left-handed?

116
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:55,470
Yes.

117
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:56,570
Didn't you say

118
00:06:56,840 --> 00:07:00,120
she uses her left hand to eat, drink water, and drive?

119
00:07:00,730 --> 00:07:01,790
When did I say that?

120
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:02,750
Yeah,

121
00:07:03,090 --> 00:07:04,680
Bai Li is not left-handed.

122
00:07:06,470 --> 00:07:08,750
How dare you play dirty with me?

123
00:07:11,330 --> 00:07:12,940
You really are pretending,

124
00:07:13,990 --> 00:07:15,270
Ning Mochen.

125
00:07:18,610 --> 00:07:19,470
Su Yu,

126
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:20,990
can you come out with me?

127
00:07:26,710 --> 00:07:27,910
She exposed herself.

128
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:29,510
If she were Bai Li,

129
00:07:29,530 --> 00:07:31,040
she should've been confused that she didn't have this habit

130
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:33,260
when I said she was left-handed.

131
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,930
Why did she start pretending instead?

132
00:07:34,930 --> 00:07:36,230
I don't understand what you're talking about.

133
00:07:36,230 --> 00:07:37,460
She's acting as Bai Li.

134
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:38,600
Senior lost her memory.

135
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,440
It's normal for her to do something abnormal.

136
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,340
On the contrary,

137
00:07:41,340 --> 00:07:42,670
why won't you let her go?

138
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,110
Don't you understand?

139
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:45,159
She's hiding something.

140
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,760
Her memory loss is fake.

141
00:07:47,370 --> 00:07:48,640
What's there for her to hide?

142
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,030
Don't you think she's different

143
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:51,510
after waking up?

144
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:53,070
A person's nature won't change

145
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:54,530
even if they have amnesia.

146
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,400
I don't understand what you're talking about.

147
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,860
Do you also think I'm different from before?

148
00:08:01,370 --> 00:08:03,370
It means your senior can change too.

149
00:08:03,590 --> 00:08:06,320
She can change into someone you don't know at all.

150
00:08:10,850 --> 00:08:12,270
Bai Li, what's wrong?

151
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,070
Are you okay?

152
00:08:14,670 --> 00:08:16,400
-Senior.
-Does your head hurt?

153
00:08:16,590 --> 00:08:17,050
Senior,

154
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:18,160
what's wrong?

155
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,840
I want to go home.

156
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:21,950
Okay.

157
00:08:22,170 --> 00:08:23,080
Let me take you home.

158
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,490
I'll take you home.

159
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:38,429
Senior.

160
00:08:39,510 --> 00:08:41,330
Ning Mochen is paranoid.

161
00:08:41,789 --> 00:08:43,530
She doesn’t trust others easily.

162
00:08:43,530 --> 00:08:44,790
Please don't mind her.

163
00:08:48,060 --> 00:08:49,920
Are you apologizing to me for her?

164
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:52,650
I don't want you to be angry because of her.

165
00:08:54,010 --> 00:08:56,290
Ning Mochen has changed a lot.

166
00:08:57,090 --> 00:08:58,690
While you were unconscious,

167
00:08:58,940 --> 00:09:00,460
she did a lot for you too.

168
00:09:03,210 --> 00:09:04,650
According to what you said,

169
00:09:04,650 --> 00:09:05,980
I should even thank her?

170
00:09:08,030 --> 00:09:11,060
But I heard she's a rich lady.

171
00:09:11,370 --> 00:09:12,970
I don't think she'd value it.

172
00:09:13,010 --> 00:09:15,340
The Ning family members are all snobbish,

173
00:09:15,470 --> 00:09:18,400
but Ning Mochen has decided to leave the Ning family.

174
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:24,210
Why?

175
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:29,160
She has a bad relationship with the Ning family.

176
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,820
She's always been oppressed.

177
00:09:30,890 --> 00:09:33,700
To Ning Zhaoxiong, she's just a pawn.

178
00:09:35,970 --> 00:09:36,800
I trust her.

179
00:09:37,050 --> 00:09:38,710
If she leaves the Ning family,

180
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,900
she will definitely have a good life.

181
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:43,660
Ning Zhaoxiong.

182
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:44,760
The Ning family.

183
00:09:46,670 --> 00:09:48,760
I will destroy you all.

184
00:09:49,170 --> 00:09:50,250
Maybe

185
00:09:50,470 --> 00:09:52,780
this is actually a good opportunity.

186
00:09:54,130 --> 00:09:56,190
Senior, what are you thinking about?

187
00:09:59,170 --> 00:09:59,980
Nothing.

188
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:01,830
I'm just thinking

189
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:05,300
that since you think highly of her,

190
00:10:05,570 --> 00:10:07,570
I should have more contact with her.

191
00:10:08,790 --> 00:10:11,030
If I can't build a good relationship with her,

192
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:12,720
things will be difficult for you.

193
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,120
If there's a conflict...

194
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:19,580
You will definitely protect her

195
00:10:20,490 --> 00:10:23,740
and I'll be sad then.

196
00:10:27,100 --> 00:10:28,230
Bai Li, don't worry.

197
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:29,840
It won't happen.

198
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:04,790
Hello?

199
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:06,590
Let's meet up.

200
00:11:09,810 --> 00:11:10,970
Who are you?

201
00:11:11,310 --> 00:11:13,640
Don't you remember your own phone number?

202
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,080
Oh.

203
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:17,110
Ms. Ning,

204
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:18,880
what can I do for you?

205
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,920
I want to treat you to dinner.

206
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:23,130
Are you free tonight?

207
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:27,570
Sure.

208
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:39,760
[Yan Wu]

209
00:11:57,470 --> 00:11:59,850
Mom, what are you doing?

210
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,510
I work here now.

211
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:06,710
How have you been?

212
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:10,350
Not bad.

213
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:15,110
Do you want to return to the Ning family?

214
00:12:16,770 --> 00:12:19,020
You know Dad's temper.

215
00:12:19,570 --> 00:12:22,060
It was hard for me too.

216
00:12:22,990 --> 00:12:25,410
He's been very busy lately.

217
00:12:26,940 --> 00:12:29,270
-Mom, after some time—
-Xi.

218
00:12:33,450 --> 00:12:35,830
Don't call me Mom anymore.

219
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,770
If you want,

220
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:41,120
you can call me Ling or Auntie.

221
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:44,900
If you think I've disgraced the Ning family,

222
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,850
you can also pretend you don't know me.

223
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:51,600
Mom,

224
00:12:51,950 --> 00:12:54,150
at that time,

225
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:56,870
Dad was also pressured by Su Yu,

226
00:12:57,190 --> 00:13:00,870
so he had to find someone to give him an explanation.

227
00:13:01,470 --> 00:13:04,120
These days, you haven't been home

228
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:06,550
and he's actually not used to it.

229
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:07,640
He misses you.

230
00:13:11,460 --> 00:13:13,120
Your dad doesn't need anyone.

231
00:13:15,300 --> 00:13:17,330
I've been with him for so long

232
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:19,310
and experienced so many things.

233
00:13:19,590 --> 00:13:21,950
If I still don't have a clear idea about what kind of person he is,

234
00:13:21,950 --> 00:13:23,810
I would be blind.

235
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:28,920
Whether it's me, you, or Ning Mochen,

236
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:31,030
we're all family,

237
00:13:31,060 --> 00:13:32,650
but we're just pawns

238
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:34,180
for him to manipulate.

239
00:13:36,830 --> 00:13:37,870
I'm fine now.

240
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,310
I've thought it through.

241
00:13:40,500 --> 00:13:42,690
I want to live the life I want now.

242
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:45,720
I used to like to play around with flowers and plants.

243
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,770
You know that too.

244
00:13:47,230 --> 00:13:49,490
I finally have a lot of time

245
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:51,430
to look into my hobbies now.

246
00:13:54,010 --> 00:13:54,870
What about you?

247
00:13:55,330 --> 00:13:57,410
You bought so many things.

248
00:13:57,830 --> 00:13:59,540
You must be running out of space at home.

249
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:02,550
You don't plan on coming back, but you're still controlling me.

250
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:03,950
I'm not controlling you.

251
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:05,400
I want to remind you

252
00:14:06,890 --> 00:14:09,050
that everything in the world

253
00:14:09,110 --> 00:14:10,500
has its price.

254
00:14:10,780 --> 00:14:12,700
Like with the things you bought,

255
00:14:13,170 --> 00:14:15,830
don't just look at their glamorous appearance.

256
00:14:16,850 --> 00:14:18,380
As a part of the Ning family,

257
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:24,000
while you're enjoying your lavish lifestyle,

258
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:26,240
you also have to be ready to

259
00:14:26,430 --> 00:14:29,190
be sacrificed and exchanged for interests at any time.

260
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:31,190
Have you really thought it through?

261
00:14:31,870 --> 00:14:33,370
Doesn't that mean

262
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:35,220
I'm worth the price?

263
00:14:36,850 --> 00:14:40,810
Should I really give up everything and start over

264
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:42,860
in order to seem noble?

265
00:14:44,070 --> 00:14:45,410
Chen Ling, time to work.

266
00:14:47,290 --> 00:14:48,240
Okay, I got it.

267
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:51,150
Xi, wait for me.

268
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:58,970
What is this?

269
00:14:59,230 --> 00:14:59,990
It's for you.

270
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:01,390
Doubtful knight's-spur.

271
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:02,550
Look at its shape.

272
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:05,370
Doesn't it look like a swallow flying freely?

273
00:15:06,950 --> 00:15:07,430
Okay,

274
00:15:07,690 --> 00:15:08,460
thank you.

275
00:15:08,830 --> 00:15:11,110
I'll visit you more in the future.

276
00:15:11,710 --> 00:15:12,730
Okay.

277
00:15:15,030 --> 00:15:16,960
This is your favorite restaurant.

278
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:18,960
I ordered your favorite dishes.

279
00:15:19,590 --> 00:15:20,310
Really?

280
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:24,180
I don't remember coming here before.

281
00:15:24,410 --> 00:15:26,210
Indeed, Bai Li hasn't been here.

282
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:27,730
I'm talking about you.

283
00:15:30,310 --> 00:15:32,480
I don't understand what you're talking about.

284
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,880
There's no one else here.

285
00:15:34,250 --> 00:15:35,540
You can stop acting,

286
00:15:36,070 --> 00:15:36,880
Ning Mochen.

287
00:15:42,710 --> 00:15:43,810
Ms. Ning,

288
00:15:44,020 --> 00:15:45,570
you're confusing me.

289
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:49,460
You and I both know the situation now,

290
00:15:50,050 --> 00:15:52,180
but I don't know what your purpose is.

291
00:15:54,190 --> 00:15:55,790
If you want to say something,

292
00:15:56,250 --> 00:15:58,180
just be straightforward about it.

293
00:15:58,450 --> 00:16:00,690
My brain has been in a mess recently.

294
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:02,420
I don't want to guess at riddles.

295
00:16:02,420 --> 00:16:05,050
You can copy me for a while,

296
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:06,950
but can you do it forever?

297
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:08,710
Why would I copy you?

298
00:16:22,640 --> 00:16:23,400
See?

299
00:16:24,210 --> 00:16:25,670
You're still used to

300
00:16:25,910 --> 00:16:28,040
picking out the mushrooms in the food.

301
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:29,950
You must've forgotten.

302
00:16:30,140 --> 00:16:31,730
You're in Bai Li's body now.

303
00:16:32,070 --> 00:16:34,330
You're no longer allergic to mushrooms.

304
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,850
What are you talking about?

305
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,830
I just don't like mushrooms.

306
00:16:41,310 --> 00:16:42,150
Ning Mochen,

307
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:44,520
you will give yourself away sooner or later.

308
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:46,380
I don’t care what your purpose is,

309
00:16:46,580 --> 00:16:49,210
but I hope you won’t hurt Su Yu with my identity.

310
00:16:49,590 --> 00:16:51,120
He has nothing against you.

311
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:52,590
Su Yu?

312
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:56,410
This junior is nice to me.

313
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:00,310
Why would I hurt him?

314
00:17:01,190 --> 00:17:02,810
What exactly do you want?

315
00:17:04,609 --> 00:17:06,069
I have no purpose.

316
00:17:06,849 --> 00:17:08,550
What I have now

317
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,900
is everything you don't have.

318
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:16,040
People will find out

319
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:18,369
what kind of person you are sooner or later.

320
00:17:18,369 --> 00:17:20,190
Even if you have Bai Li's body,

321
00:17:20,319 --> 00:17:21,980
you'll always be Ning Mochen.

322
00:17:34,190 --> 00:17:35,510
In that case,

323
00:17:37,080 --> 00:17:38,760
I'll tell you the truth.

324
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:41,340
No matter who I am,

325
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:45,400
you'll always be that

326
00:17:46,430 --> 00:17:47,660
promiscuous,

327
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,150
ignorant,

328
00:17:49,620 --> 00:17:50,830
and crazy

329
00:17:51,270 --> 00:17:52,980
home-wrecker.

330
00:17:53,950 --> 00:17:55,960
The one hated by everyone,

331
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:59,540
Ning Mochen.

332
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:05,030
Give me back my bracelet!

333
00:18:05,190 --> 00:18:05,920
Give it to me!

334
00:18:06,180 --> 00:18:07,260
-Give it back!
-Give it to me!

335
00:18:07,260 --> 00:18:07,990
Give it to me!

336
00:18:11,910 --> 00:18:12,770
Senior.

337
00:18:13,260 --> 00:18:13,990
Are you okay?

338
00:18:15,050 --> 00:18:16,060
What did you do?

339
00:18:16,410 --> 00:18:17,960
She fell down herself.

340
00:18:19,190 --> 00:18:19,940
Come. Get up.

341
00:18:22,080 --> 00:18:22,950
Are you okay?

342
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:27,110
You all become hesitant when mentioning about me and Ye Yunkai,

343
00:18:27,130 --> 00:18:28,920
