344
00:18:29,330 --> 00:18:32,420
It was her.

345
00:18:33,080 --> 00:18:34,730
She was the one who seduced my husband

346
00:18:34,730 --> 00:18:36,120
and ruined my family.

347
00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:37,850
I know you are good friends,

348
00:18:37,950 --> 00:18:39,220
so I came.

349
00:18:39,510 --> 00:18:40,170
But then...

350
00:18:40,190 --> 00:18:41,750
She kept forcing and provoking me

351
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:43,040
again and again,

352
00:18:43,150 --> 00:18:44,470
so I dissed her back.

353
00:18:44,540 --> 00:18:45,560
Then she grabbed my hand.

354
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:46,890
Stop talking nonsense.

355
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,550
Did you call Su Yu here?

356
00:18:48,630 --> 00:18:49,470
You deliberately provoked me

357
00:18:49,470 --> 00:18:50,600
