358
00:18:50,600 --> 00:18:51,270
Enough!

359
00:18:56,310 --> 00:18:57,150
Ning Mochen,

360
00:18:59,040 --> 00:19:00,280
I was wrong about you.

361
00:19:16,150 --> 00:19:16,830
Senior.

362
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,280
Here, Senior.

363
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:26,990
Thank you.

364
00:19:31,710 --> 00:19:32,670
So,

365
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:37,430
I had an accident because of Ye Yunkai and Ning Mochen.

366
00:19:38,860 --> 00:19:40,520
No wonder every time I see her,

367
00:19:41,350 --> 00:19:42,800
I feel uncomfortable.

368
00:19:44,870 --> 00:19:45,790
Maybe

369
00:19:46,370 --> 00:19:48,900
my subconscious is protecting myself.

370
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:51,980
It doesn't want me

371
00:19:52,530 --> 00:19:55,530
to see the third person who intervened in my marriage.

372
00:20:01,870 --> 00:20:03,530
Luckily, you were here today.

373
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:04,870
Otherwise,

374
00:20:05,030 --> 00:20:06,820
I might have been badly hurt.

375
00:20:07,320 --> 00:20:08,800
She was so cruel.

376
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:25,370
She insisted on snatching this silver bracelet today.

377
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:27,990
I know

378
00:20:28,350 --> 00:20:29,950
this is your kind intention.

379
00:20:32,630 --> 00:20:33,510
But

380
00:20:34,830 --> 00:20:36,560
she is your fiancée, after all.

381
00:20:36,890 --> 00:20:38,490
You should give this to her.

382
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:39,200
Senior,

383
00:20:41,360 --> 00:20:42,650
since I gave it to you,

384
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:45,140
I have no intention of taking it back.

385
00:20:45,270 --> 00:20:45,990
Besides,

386
00:20:46,530 --> 00:20:48,390
my relationship with Ning Mochen

387
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:50,160
isn't what you think.

388
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,620
She must be mad at you today.

389
00:20:57,130 --> 00:20:58,090
I'm sorry.

390
00:20:59,210 --> 00:21:00,330
I don't want to

391
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,490
affect your relationship.

392
00:21:02,570 --> 00:21:03,900
Senior, don't say that.

393
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,370
It's getting late.

394
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:09,410
I have to go back.

395
00:21:09,620 --> 00:21:10,860
Don’t think too much.

396
00:21:14,990 --> 00:21:15,750
Su Yu.

397
00:21:22,430 --> 00:21:23,260
Nothing.

398
00:21:24,290 --> 00:21:27,090
Go and accompany the person you want to accompany.

399
00:21:44,630 --> 00:21:46,960
Since I'm Bai Li now,

400
00:21:46,990 --> 00:21:49,910
maybe I should change my plan

401
00:21:49,930 --> 00:21:52,190
to deal with Ningmei and Ning Zhaoxiong.

402
00:21:52,480 --> 00:21:55,210
Su Yu’s attitude is wavering now.

403
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:57,110
Ye Yunkai is missing too.

404
00:21:58,240 --> 00:22:00,510
I can’t count on them now.

405
00:22:01,150 --> 00:22:04,320
Looks like I need someone else

406
00:22:04,690 --> 00:22:07,210
to help me complete my plan.

407
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:11,110
As for the candidate,

408
00:22:13,510 --> 00:22:16,470
it'll depend on Ms. Bai Li's charm.

409
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:40,000
Why are you here?

410
00:22:42,460 --> 00:22:43,660
I was just passing by

411
00:22:44,170 --> 00:22:45,370
and came to visit you.

412
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:48,520
Did you come

413
00:22:49,430 --> 00:22:50,890
from your senior's place?

414
00:23:00,100 --> 00:23:01,000
Ning Mochen.

415
00:23:06,030 --> 00:23:07,110
Can we talk?

416
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,300
About what?

417
00:23:10,390 --> 00:23:11,780
How she talks about me,

418
00:23:12,230 --> 00:23:13,190
how bad I am,

419
00:23:13,190 --> 00:23:13,880
how shameless,

420
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:14,950
and how evil, right?

421
00:23:14,950 --> 00:23:16,010
It's not like that.

422
00:23:16,910 --> 00:23:17,870
She said

423
00:23:18,150 --> 00:23:20,680
she doesn't want to affect our relationship.

424
00:23:21,740 --> 00:23:23,000
If you put it like that,

425
00:23:23,850 --> 00:23:25,350
then I'm the horrible one.

426
00:23:30,590 --> 00:23:32,990
You've been criticizing her all this time.

427
00:23:33,390 --> 00:23:34,280
Then tell me

428
00:23:35,110 --> 00:23:36,370
what's wrong with her.

429
00:23:39,610 --> 00:23:40,500
Su Yu,

430
00:23:41,630 --> 00:23:43,490
she is using your feelings for her

431
00:23:43,650 --> 00:23:44,510
to control you.

432
00:23:45,100 --> 00:23:47,960
She doesn't want us to get into a relationship again.

433
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:49,160
Why would she do that?

434
00:23:51,080 --> 00:23:52,590
There can be many reasons.

435
00:23:53,870 --> 00:23:54,710
For example,

436
00:23:56,140 --> 00:23:58,270
she doesn't want us to be how we are now.

437
00:23:59,200 --> 00:24:00,770
How we are now?

438
00:24:02,910 --> 00:24:04,710
Why would she interfere in this?

439
00:24:04,990 --> 00:24:06,100
Or maybe

440
00:24:06,630 --> 00:24:08,110
she just doesn't like me.

441
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:11,400
Or maybe she didn't lose her memory

442
00:24:12,110 --> 00:24:13,440
and just wants revenge.

443
00:24:13,560 --> 00:24:14,890
Any reason is possible.

444
00:24:15,800 --> 00:24:17,430
She's not like that.

445
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:19,870
She has been trying hard to forgive you.

446
00:24:19,870 --> 00:24:21,410
It's just that she can't do it so quickly.

447
00:24:21,410 --> 00:24:23,870
Why did you come here if you don't believe me?

448
00:24:31,990 --> 00:24:33,050
Then I'll leaving.

449
00:24:34,030 --> 00:24:37,190
Su Yu and Cha still believe in the Bai Li they see more.

450
00:24:38,150 --> 00:24:40,240
The more I want to expose Ning Mochen,

451
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:42,170
the more she'll seem innocent.

452
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:44,310
I can't be impatient.

453
00:24:57,110 --> 00:24:57,880
Ms. Bai.

454
00:25:20,470 --> 00:25:22,600
Ms. Bai, how have you been recovering?

455
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:25,760
My body has recovered,

456
00:25:28,260 --> 00:25:30,110
but my brain

457
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:32,310
feels like it's in a mess.

458
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:36,790
You just experienced some trauma.

459
00:25:37,490 --> 00:25:39,350
While you were in a coma,

460
00:25:39,760 --> 00:25:41,950
your subconscious mind occupied your brain,

461
00:25:41,950 --> 00:25:44,150
causing your neurons to be disordered,

462
00:25:44,160 --> 00:25:46,830
so there are some cluttered messages.

463
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:50,540
Do you want to continue the previous treatment?

464
00:25:53,140 --> 00:25:54,140
What do you think?

465
00:25:56,530 --> 00:25:58,080
As the doctor,

466
00:25:59,630 --> 00:26:01,810
I can only give advice about whether to continue or not.

467
00:26:01,810 --> 00:26:04,200
The final decision is still up to you.

468
00:26:06,720 --> 00:26:08,840
Dr. Peng, you mean

469
00:26:09,810 --> 00:26:12,930
whether we should continue or not

470
00:26:13,140 --> 00:26:15,270
depends on me, right?

471
00:26:17,850 --> 00:26:18,670
Of course.

472
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:25,350
You always encounter people with broken hearts

473
00:26:25,430 --> 00:26:27,270
or those who are not happy with work.

474
00:26:27,270 --> 00:26:28,560
Isn't it boring?

475
00:26:28,870 --> 00:26:30,600
Ms. Bai, you're very humorous.

476
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,910
Since they come here,

477
00:26:33,060 --> 00:26:35,130
I obviously hope I can help them.

478
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:38,610
Then you probably look forward to

479
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:41,390
some more extreme or crazier patients.

480
00:26:41,590 --> 00:26:44,620
Wouldn't that show your skills as a doctor more?

481
00:26:45,770 --> 00:26:50,540
Doctors and patients are more like friends.

482
00:26:51,090 --> 00:26:53,250
Of course, I also hope to meet someone

483
00:26:53,490 --> 00:26:55,010
who fits me well,

484
00:26:55,790 --> 00:26:57,650
but treating patients

485
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:01,850
or being able to help them completely

486
00:27:01,870 --> 00:27:03,160
is my biggest wish.

487
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,240
Do you think I'm sick?

488
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:26,600
In terms of conditions,

489
00:27:27,510 --> 00:27:29,310
you do have some.

490
00:27:30,590 --> 00:27:33,210
That's why you need a psychologist like me.

491
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:36,950
What if a psychologist gets sick?

492
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:41,140
A doctor can't treat himself.

493
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:44,210
When a psychologist gets sick,

494
00:27:45,190 --> 00:27:47,720
we also need to prescribe the right medicine.

495
00:27:51,600 --> 00:27:54,320
Have you found your medicine?

496
00:28:05,060 --> 00:28:06,590
I don't want to drink water.

497
00:28:12,100 --> 00:28:13,560
Don't drink yours either.

498
00:28:15,620 --> 00:28:18,250
I remember... Where do you put your wine?

499
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:31,290
I found it.

500
00:29:04,070 --> 00:29:04,950
Dr. Peng,

501
00:29:05,190 --> 00:29:06,060
what's wrong?

502
00:29:07,110 --> 00:29:08,380
Is something wrong?

503
00:29:09,380 --> 00:29:10,180
No.

504
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:14,790
Ms. Bai, I remember you didn't drink wine before.

505
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:19,580
Maybe it's like what you said.

506
00:29:19,590 --> 00:29:22,390
Some changes happened after sleeping for so long.

507
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:33,350
This kind of alcoholic and stimulating drink

508
00:29:34,120 --> 00:29:37,630
will affect your nerve transmission

509
00:29:38,050 --> 00:29:39,740
and aggravate your condition.

510
00:29:39,740 --> 00:29:41,340
I suggest you quit drinking.

511
00:29:45,530 --> 00:29:46,210
Cheers.

512
00:29:54,460 --> 00:29:55,350
By the way,

513
00:29:55,820 --> 00:29:57,150
I have a present for you.

514
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:28,270
A normal life

515
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,540
and boring work...

516
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:34,560
You've long been tired of it.

517
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:38,510
Actually, deep down,

518
00:30:39,460 --> 00:30:41,990
you look forward to something more exciting.

519
00:30:42,730 --> 00:30:44,290
I told you long ago

520
00:30:47,670 --> 00:30:48,590
that I

521
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:51,750
am your medicine.

522
00:31:00,630 --> 00:31:04,430
A psychologist that fell in love with his patient.

523
00:31:04,500 --> 00:31:06,180
Would this scandal

524
00:31:06,740 --> 00:31:08,030
be exciting enough?

525
00:31:09,010 --> 00:31:11,820
Or maybe I can change the title to

526
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:16,740
"Psychologist Sexually Harasses His Patient."

527
00:31:17,540 --> 00:31:21,410
Wouldn't that be more eye-catching?

528
00:31:23,230 --> 00:31:24,350
Ning Mochen,

529
00:31:26,140 --> 00:31:27,590
what do you want?

530
00:31:27,990 --> 00:31:29,330
I'm threatening you,

531
00:31:29,810 --> 00:31:31,900
so you have to listen to me.

532
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:42,010
What's wrong?

533
00:31:42,460 --> 00:31:43,770
Is something bothering you?

534
00:31:43,770 --> 00:31:45,370
Ye Yunkai has gone bankrupt.

535
00:31:46,280 --> 00:31:48,120
You can't use him anymore.

536
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:50,260
You're already Bai Li.

537
00:31:50,280 --> 00:31:51,780
Are you still going to go after the Ning family?

538
00:31:51,780 --> 00:31:52,780
You can't

539
00:31:53,360 --> 00:31:55,400
compete with Ning Zhaoxiong now.

540
00:31:58,380 --> 00:32:01,310
I have you, Dr. Peng.

541
00:32:05,290 --> 00:32:07,280
Let's obliterate Ningmei Jewelry

542
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:11,510
together.

543
00:32:13,710 --> 00:32:15,410
The show has just started.

544
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,730
The good stuff is still coming up.
